## 🎬 Анимации

### Scroll-reveal
```css
@keyframes fadeInUp {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}
```

### Letter-spacing
```css
@keyframes letterSpacing {
  from {
    letter-spacing: -0.5em;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    letter-spacing: 0;
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
```

### Wave animations
```css
@keyframes wave1 {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateX(50px) translateY(-20px); }
}
```

